Why does MC need my personal info?: Hikwalahokayini MC yi lava vuxokoxoko bya mina?
Who can see my personal info?: I mani a vonaka vuxokoxoko lebyi?
How can I see, change or delete my perso: Ndzi byi vona njhani, ku cinca/ku sula?
How long does MC keep my info?: MC yi byi hlayisa nkarhi wo tanihi kwihi?
MC is a Health Department programme. It: MomConnect i nongonoko wa Ndzawulo ya Rihanyu. Yi rhumela swihungwana eka wena & ricece. Ku vona, ku cinca kumbe ku sula vuxokoxoko, dayila *134*550*7#
MomConnect needs your personal info to s: MomConnect yi lava vuxokoxoko bya wena ku ku rhumela swihungwana leswi fambelanaka na xiyimo xa vuyimani bya wena kumbe vukhale bya ricece ra wena. Hi ku tiva laha u tsariseke MomConnect kona, Ndzawulo yi nga tiyisisa leswaku vavasati va nyikiwa vukorhokeri etliliniki ya ka n'wina. Ku tiva laha u tsariseke kona swi pfuna Ndzawulo ku tirhana na swihoyozelo/swivilelo eka MomConnect mayelana na ntokoto wa wena wa le tliliniki.
MomConnect collects your phone and ID nu: MomConnect yi teka tinomboro ta wena ta riqingho & ta Pasi, ndhawu ya tliliniki & vuxokoxoko mayelana na hilaha vuyimani bya wena byi fambaka hakona.
MomConnect is owned and run by the Healt: MomConnect i ya Ndzawulo ya Rihanyu naswona yi fambisiwa hi yona. MTN, Cell C, Telkom, Vodacom, Praekelt, Jembi, HISP na WhatsApp (ya Facebook) ti hlengeleta na ku phurosesa data ya wena hi ku yimela yona.
You can see, change, or ask us to delete: U nga vona, u cinca kumbe u hi kombela ku sula vuxokoxoko bya wena hi ku dayila *134*550*7#
MomConnect will automatically delete you: MomConnect yi ta sula xikan'wekan'we vuxokoxoko lebyi 7 wa malembe na 9 wa tin'hweti endzhaku ka loko u tsarisile.
Sorry, that number is not recognised. Di: Hi khomele, nomboro leyi a yi tiveki. Dayila nomboro leyi u rhangeke u tsarisa yona. Ku cinca nomboro, dayila *134*550*7# kumbe u tsarisa nakambe etliliniki.
